[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1m   USE CASE 3 — a paid skill marketplace, no human in the loop\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.208, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 14 · A peer advertises a skill, with a price\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m   criterion: F7/F8 — agents discover each other via A2A cards\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[2.457, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  peer B card:   skill compute.run · price 5 LEZ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;37m  id  Private/BC44Y7y8XLMyqUbbAUis4UT4M6…\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Discoverable over Logos Messaging, with a declared LEZ price.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.807, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 15 · The agent hires it — and pays, by itself\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F8 — two agents: discover → task → autonomous LEZ payment\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[2.469, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  before:  agent 80 LEZ    peer B 0 LEZ\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.006, "o", "\u001b[1m$ logoscore call agent_module agent_task <B-card> compute.run\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.265, "o", "  task task_162227807669500_0 · price 5 · status submitted\r\n"]
[5.032, "o", "  → transfer proof generated\r\n  → transfer proof generated\r\n"]
[10.499, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  after:   agent \u001b[1;32m75\u001b[0m\u001b[0;37m LEZ    peer B \u001b[1;32m5\u001b[0m\u001b[0;37m LEZ\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Agent-to-agent payment SETTLED — −5 from its own funds, +5 to the peer. No human, no processor.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.809, "o", "\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m▌ 16 · Over the limit? It asks first\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m   criterion: F5 — above-threshold spend is held for owner approval\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[2.408, "o", "\u001b[1m$ agent_task at price 80   (limit is 50)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.209, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  80 > 50  →  pending_approval\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;37m  reason: spend exceeds autonomous threshold — NOT sent\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;32m   ✓ Autonomy under the limit, owner approval above it.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
